briefTitle: Study of the Safety of Use of Intravitreal SOK583A1 Provided in a Prefilled Syringe
officialTitle: An Open-label, Single-arm, Multicenter Study in Patients With Neovascular Age-related Macular Degeneration to Evaluate the Safety of SOK583A1 (40 mg/mL), a Proposed Aflibercept Biosimilar Product, Provided in a Prefilled Syringe
summary: This was an open-label, single arm, multicenter, Phase IIIb study in subjects with (wet) nAMD, eligible for IVT aflibercept treatment.

primaryOutcome.measure: Number of Participants With Ocular Treatment Emergent Adverse Events
